Different Use Cases

•	Navigation Subsystem
  o	Using current location
  o	Using starting point
  o	Enter end point
  o	Directions to destination
  o	Find fastest path
  o	Find lecture hall
  o	Search for locations
  o	Saving locations
  o	Determine pedestrian traffic

•	Login Subsystem
  o	Student Login
  o	Lecturer Login
  o	Delete account
  o	Users interests

•	Rewards Subsystem
  o	Determine steps walked
  o	Setting goals
  o	Compare step count against other users
  o	Leaderboard 

•	Guest Subsystem
  o	Point of interests


•	Admin Subsystem
  o	System usage statistics

•	Point of Interest/ Events Subsystem
  o	Determine close points of interest
  o	Determine events nearby
